    "New York City Subway Lines, 2009 is a line theme representing the New York City subway lines. Attribute data include the names of the lines and indication whether the segments of the lines are above or below ground. The raw data for the line files is from the New York State Department of Transportation. Files are provided in the projection NAD83 to align with the NYCMap basemap."
